data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to your dream waterfront oasis on Sunset Beach in Treasure Island! This captivating 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom elevated home has undergone a stunning transformation, making it the epitome of coastal charm and comfort.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a meticulously remodeled interior. The entire home boasts new features, including hardy plank siding and many new impact-rated windows, ensuring both durability and timeless curb appeal. The heart of the home, the kitchen, has been completely reinvented, showcasing a breathtaking marble slab countertop, complemented by a suite of stainless steel appliances.    New Cali bamboo floors are not only environmentally conscious, but also extremely durable. Every detail has been carefully considered, from the custom handmade wood doors, vanities, and wall cabinets to the thoughtful choice of the new exterior trex decking on the balconies. The landscape has been reimagined with beach pebbles that feel great beneath your feet, creating a low-maintenance outdoor haven.    This charming retreat is ideally located at the end of a peaceful street with minimal traffic, ensuring a safe and serene environment for your family. Let your worries drift away as you savor the awe-inspiring views that embrace you from nearly every room in the house.    When it's time to venture beyond your private retreat, you'll find yourself mere steps away from one of the best beaches in the world as well as a number of restaurants and bars. Whether by foot or a relaxing ride on the water, your entertainment options are boundless.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary waterfront residence your new home. Immerse yourself in the allure of Sunset Beach and discover a life of tranquility, beauty, and endless enjoyment. Schedule your viewing today and experience the magic for yourself!
